Third Department,

January, 1973

(January 3, 1973) In the Matter of John M. Keane, as Surrogate of Broome County, Petitioner.

Application for an order, pursuant to section 89 of the Judiciary Law, directing the destruction of certain records granted. Herlihy, P. J., Staley, Jr., Greenblott, Cooke and Sweeney, JJ., concur.
